headline.main: Malaysian PM Chides North Korea, as 'Rude' Envoy Sent Packing
headline.print_headline: Malaysian PM Chides North Korea, as 'Rude' Envoy Sent Packing

lead_paragraph: Malaysian Prime Minister Najib Razak rebuked North Korea on Monday as his government expelled its envoy for casting doubt over the impartiality of the investigation into the bizarre murder of the North Korean leader's estranged half brother.
